description: There's no better way to turn your good times into great times than with fantastic food, and that's exactly what you'll get with Cherry Bomb Bus! Owner and operator Chef Jennifer Zavala will bring her culinary expertise to you and your guests' taste buds with a custom menu made especially for you. If you want to bring something exceptional to the table for your next event, then Cherry Bomb Bus is the food truck for you!
name: Cherry Bomb Bus
